<br>
there has been some heated arguments going on at Monkly buisness, and these are the points that have been made<br>
<br>
Monks became somewhat overpowered, after Velious and those all/all 100hp 15 ac 0.1 weight items! <br>
<br>
my monk tanks better than my guilds best warrior!<br>
<br>
even after the nurf warriors will still be sucky taunters!<br>
<br>
Nurfing monks does not make warriors more powerful!<br>
it makes groups weaker!<br>
<br>
as i see it this whole nurf the monks because they are overpowered compared to the Tank classes is like rewarding a child with a prize then taking it away because it would make his siblings upset!<br>
<br>
the problem is not that monks are too powerful, it is that warriors are too weak!! <br>
<br>
think about it! how many times have you seen other classes get boosts and warriors get nothing!!<br>
<br>
in the beginning the warrior was the Tank! hands down! if any other class tryed to tank they died!<br>
<br>
but through VI's own poor insight and bad planning Rangers, Monks, SKs, and Pallies can and in many instances out tank a Warrior with like items!<br>
<br>
I play a Monk on Prexus! and have had a standing Challenge to which only one warrior has met! <br>
100pp to any warrior that can steal aggro from me!<br>
only one has done it! <br>
i started this challenge at lvl 18! I am now 43, and only ONE freaking warrior has ever stolen aggro for a whole fight from me! <br>
he was a 53 barb in half crusty armor, wielding Lammies! it was his second try after Epics couldnt do it!<br>
<br>
so instead of giving Warriors a well earned Boost in DPS  taunting abilities and better Items they give them piss poor PoP AAs like &quot;meatshield&quot;<br>
and Nurf the monks that have worked hard to get to where they are, <br>
<br>
ive played 3 warriors, a barb, a dwarf and a gnome (latter for fun rather than serious play)<br>
and have been very disappointed at their taunting abilities and DPS, i played the gnome to 40, the barb 20 and the Dwarf to 43, <br>
<br>
i think warriors get the second coolest role in the game...second to pulling =) they get to tank....they are the plate covered T-bone steak taking the DMG so that others dont have to! but through VI's poor planning their Tanking status is threatened!<br>
<br>
what should be done? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ukaldanm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>kaldanm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 25<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/12/02 4:41:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1402.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://pubkal.free.fr/images/clan.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: you dont make a warrior a tank by nurfing other Classes!</span><hr size=1> *Cough*<br>
